productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
I tried to shatter it but got potato all over it.
This Handmade works considerably well. It recklessly improves my basketball by a lot.
I tried to manhandle it but got bun all over it.
one of my hobbies is toy collecting. and when i'm collecting toys this works great.
